---
import Layout from "../layout/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Shipping and Delivery Policy | Neurotechh"
  description="Shipping and Delivery Policy for Neurotechh - Learn about our shipping methods, delivery times, and related policies."
  imgurl="https://neurotechh.xyz/seo.png"
>
  <section class="min-h-[80vh] w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 mt-[12vh]">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-incognito font-semibold text-brandred mb-8">
      Shipping and Delivery Policy
    </h1>
    
    <article class="prose prose-lg prose-invert prose-headings:text-brandred prose-headings:font-incognito prose-headings:font-semibold prose-p:text-text/80 prose-a:text-brandpink hover:prose-a:text-brandred prose-strong:text-brandred">
      <p class="text-lg">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <h2>1. Digital Products and Services</h2>
      <p>
        For our digital products and services:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access is granted immediately upon successful payment</li>
        <li>Login credentials will be sent to your registered email address</li>
        <li>Technical support is available during business hours</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Physical Products</h2>
      <p>
        For physical products (if applicable):
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Processing time: 1-2 business days</li>
        <li>Shipping time: 3-7 business days within India</li>
        <li>International shipping: 7-14 business days</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Shipping Methods</h2>
      <p>
        We use reliable shipping partners to ensure safe and timely delivery:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Standard Shipping: 3-7 business days</li>
        <li>Express Shipping: 1-3 business days</li>
        <li>International Shipping: Available to select countries</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Tracking Information</h2>
      <p>
        Once your order is shipped, you will receive:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Shipping confirmation email with tracking number</li>
        <li>Real-time tracking updates</li>
        <li>Estimated delivery date</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Delivery Issues</h2>
      <p>
        In case of delivery issues:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact us within 48 hours of the expected delivery date</li>
        <li>Provide your order number and tracking information</li>
        <li>We will investigate and resolve the issue promptly</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>
        For any shipping or delivery related queries, please contact us at:
        <br />
        <a href="mailto:contact@neurotechh.xyz">contact@neurotechh.xyz</a>
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout> 